==個人生活==
1999年7月28日林沃德嫁給法國作家Valéry Lameignère，2002年離婚<ref>Agger, Michael (May 21, 2005). [http://nymag.com/nymetro/arts/theater/10522/ "Don't You Forget About Me"] {{Wayback|url=http://nymag.com/nymetro/arts/theater/10522/ |date=20210227133914 }}. nymag.com. Retrieved May 24, 2011.</ref>，隔年生下一個女兒叫馬蒂爾達；2007年她嫁給美國作家Panio Gianopoulos，2009年生下雙胞胎阿黛爾和羅馬。她懷孕被写进《[[青春密語|青春密語]]》的故事情節。<ref>[http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20250221,00.html Molly Ringwald Expecting Twins] {{Wayback|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20250221,00.html |date=20160812120905 }} People, January 23, 2009</ref>

